Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.88,0:01:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Dr. David Hawkins. I've been a psychiatrist for 35 years, worked for many years in the field of psychoanalysis, all the various forms of individual and group psychotherapy, did years of research in psychopharmacology, also in nutrition and its relationship to brain chemistry, many years I worked with addiction, and for the last 10 years I've been working on research in the nature of consciousness itself and its application of that human field of knowledge.\Nknowledge known as the spiritual. And so we've done a series of talks on utilizing a consciousness approach to a variety of man's problems, you know, stress, alcoholism, various diseases, depression, fear, major loss, and in those talks we've spent a great deal of time on the subject matter and a short amount of time on the map of consciousness that we've utilized in all of them to explain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that relationship between body, mind, and spirit, which is so important to understand in self-healing. And in the talk we did on self-healing, we went into that rather extensively with some practical applications clinically and from my own life.\NAnd so people have asked to have perhaps a talk on just the map of consciousness itself, without any special application to any particular human problem. But the implications of it are, and from an understanding of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.62,0:02:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,its application to all human problems becomes rather apparent. And so I want to talk today then, we'll be talking from this chart which we have before. This is a map of consciousness. It's extremely useful. It came out of a composite of 10 years of research in a variety of fields. And that's a subject in itself. It's a mathematical model. And as far as we know, the first time that many of these energy fields have been\Ncalibrated. When we're talking about consciousness, then we're talking about energy fields. And so to begin with then, within the box, this box here, we have general levels of consciousness, fields of consciousness. And these have been calibrated as to the direction of the field as indicated by the arrows, those below courage, all going to the left. Those above courage, the energy fields all go to the right. What's the significance of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.52,0:03:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely. So we have the significance of that direction of the energy field, the same as it is in geomancy. That which is in a negative direction does not support life, is anti-life you might say. That which is in a positive direction, in the direction of the\Ntruth, just as this is the direction of that which is false, supports life and nurtures life. And so the top of the box, we approach an alignment with truth, we
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.06,0:03:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,see that the energy fields become more powerful. And that they're\Nnormally
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Numerical calibration becomes higher\NThe calibration of the fields goes as follows starting with death at zero
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If we calibrate the relative power of these energy fields, we will end up with what the world calls enlightenment at about 600\NEnlightenment meaning that one is transcended duality transcended the identification with a small personal self and so within the box
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm, these levels are what the person generally means when they talk about me or myself and therefore it is the ego\NIt is the self with a small s just as beyond the top of the box is the self with a capital S
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to the right of the energy field\NAre the emotions that are usually experienced coming out of that energy field?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And to the right of that is the process going on in consciousness\NTo the left of these energy fields we have the view of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,one's perception the perception that comes from that general level of consciousness and\Nthe view of God the kind of a God that would be the god of that kind of a world perception and
