Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.49,0:21:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They're now able to face things, face and cope and handle,\Nand the first time they're able to be appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.49,0:21:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So all these energy fields below here, you see,\Ncourage still will experience these lesser feelings, these negative feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But the person in courage now has the power,\Nto handle those negative energies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the process that's critical is one of empowerment.\NThe person becomes re-empowered by telling the truth.
